        <p>The convergence of drone, AR, and AI technologies presents a unique opportunity. The global drone market is projected to reach $63.6 billion by 2025, growing at a CAGR of 14.2%. The AR market is expected to reach $198 billion by 2025, growing at a CAGR of 46.6%. The AI market is expected to surpass $190 billion by 2025. This convergence creates a powerful platform for real-time data analysis and intelligent decision-making.</p>
    </section>

